{
  "stem": "12053.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our parents had prepared us in that way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And later on-- you know the work I'm doing, I've done for the last few years, is to research on the Kindertransport and my talks about it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all these things, I found out later, what had really happened and that all the parents promised their children it won't be for long, and especially the little children.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents told me that all being well, they will come and join us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- or they'll go to America.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or they'll go to Palestine or whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we'll meet again in a few weeks or a few months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you have a wonderful time in England.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You learn a new language and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I supposed the lords and ladies were marching around the street there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother always thought he'd become a lord.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sister thought she'd become an English lady and dressed up in those beautiful uniforms, the-- because I think it was only two years earlier-- it was 1937-- that we saw photographs of Princess Elizabeth and the little-- and Margaret with their parents when he was-- I think it was 1937-- when the king was crowned, when the other King abdicated, right?",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, of course, the news spread over Germany as well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Must have bought some magazines then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it interested us very much, reading about all that was going on in England.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, we thought we'd would join all the aristocracy in England.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, well, we never did, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we came to England and--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the suitcase, my parents-- my parents packed the suitcase.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was sort of a specified by the committee, by the Jewish committee, what was to be packed.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
